data.description: Nestled on a vast 45-acre expanse, this property effortlessly marries pastoral charm with forested tranquility, all while adjoining Pisgah National Forest. Within its bounds, a considerable portion is dedicated to fenced pasture, seamlessly blending into woodlands. At the heart of this gem is the quintessential 3 bedroom, 1 bath farmhouse, straight out of a design magazine, exuding refined country elegance.  Inside, an updated kitchen & gleaming hardwood floors elevate its appeal. Accentuating the primary residence is a historic 4-stall barn, evoking rustic nostalgia. Meadow Fork Creek, which spans the front border of the property, is a bold trout stream & stocking point & is complemented by a picturesque cabana for waterside relaxation.  Additional features include fiber optic internet, a bluff with a dedicated septic system & camper hookup, interwoven trails, 14 inherent springs, & a diverse array of outbuildings. With furnishings negotiable this estate is ready for its next chapter.
